OSSEC Host-Based Intrusion Detection Setup (Playbook)

> System: Kali Linux
> Author: Narkis
> Tool: OSSEC HIDS
> Goal: Install and configure OSSEC to monitor logs, detect suspicious activity (e.g., failed SSH logins), and test rule triggering.

